flowchart LR
  H[Harm or disputed outcome] --> IN[Intake and identity protection]
  IN --> TR[Triage and responsible body]
  TR --> PR[Preserve evidence and pause effects where justified]
  PR --> RV[Review]
  RV --> DE[Decision and explanation]
  DE --> RM[Correction or remedy]
  RM --> AP[Appeal or external escalation]
  AP --> CL[Closure and systemic learning]
